data.description: Location!!! Location!!! Location!!! UCR NEIGHBORHOOD of Riverside. This magnificent single story, corner lot home has quite a bit of features to offer. This home offers 4 spacious bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, upgraded kitchen with espresso no-slam cabinets & quartz countertops. NEW CARPET (September 2023) in 3 bedrooms, NEW (September 2023) PAINT in 4 of the bedrooms. NEW (Sep. 2023) Quartz Countertops, SINK, & FAUCET in bathrooms. From entering into the home with a large open kitchen with dining area to the spacious living room featuring (gas) a cozy fireplace during the holidays. If you are looking to entertain, look no further, this home features a large lot with room to grow, whether it's adding a pool/jacuzzi, built in bbq, or adding some concrete in the front left yard for RV parking you will be sure to know that the opportunities are endless. The proximity of this home to UCR (1.1 mile away), University Village shopping center, & schools makes this home highly desirable. Come tour this home today.
